OL,3,CNational Lottery on the lookout for
OL,4,Cmystery Set For Life winner in
OL,5,CDerbyshire
OL,7,FThe lucky ticket matched all five main
OL,8,Fnumbers 3, 21, 22, 28 and 38 in the
OL,9,Fdraw on Monday, May 18, 2026.
OL,11,FThey now have until November 14, 2026,
OL,12,Fto claim their prize and lottery
OL,13,Fbosses are urging people to dig out
OL,14,Ftheir tickets to see if they have
OL,15,Fscooped the prize.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1780405873
OL,3,CNational Lottery on the lookout for
OL,4,Cmystery Set For Life winner in
OL,5,CDerbyshire
OL,7,FAndy Carter, senior winners' advisor
OL,8,Fat Allwyn, operator of The National
OL,9,FLottery, said: "We're calling on
OL,10,Fplayers who may have bought a ticket
OL,11,Fin the Borough of Amber Valley for the
OL,12,FSet for Life draw on 18 May to check
OL,13,Fand double check their tickets.
OL,15,F"Do you live in the borough or were
OL,16,Fyou passing through? You could be our
OL,17,Fmissing winner. We'd like nothing more
OL,18,Fthan to unite our mystery ticket-
OL,19,Fholder with their incredible prize."
OL,26,@qD@POUwD@AOU{D@dO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
