OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1780405873
OL,3,CNational Lottery on the lookout for
OL,4,Cmystery Set For Life winner in
OL,5,CDerbyshire
OL,7,FAnyone not in possession of their
OL,8,Fticket, for whatever reason, but who
OL,9,Fbelieves they have a genuine claim can
OL,10,Fstill make a claim in writing to
OL,11,FAllwyn, but it must be within 30 days
OL,12,Fof the draw.
OL,14,FIf no-one comes forward with the
OL,15,Fwinning ticket before the prize claim
OL,16,Fdeadline, then the prize money, plus
OL,17,Fall the interest it has generated,
OL,18,Fwill go to help National Lottery-
OL,19,Ffunded projects across the UK.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
